your daughter's wedding with the rest?

531
01:03:53,796 --> 01:03:56,663
I speak the truth, sir!
I've brought all I had!

532
01:03:57,033 --> 01:04:02,630
We need just one bullet
to blow your brains out!

533
01:04:03,005 --> 01:04:04,939
The stinking bastard!

534
01:04:08,878 --> 01:04:11,847
And what have you got, Dholiya?
- It's wheat, sir.

535
01:04:12,915 --> 01:04:15,816
Very well. Keep all the stuff there.

536
01:04:16,686 --> 01:04:17,744
Hold it.

537
01:04:19,355 --> 01:04:23,917
Welcome, Thakur!
You're still alive, are you?

538
01:04:25,561 --> 01:04:28,962
Yes. And till such time
as I live...

539
