tell Gabbar you won't even
get a grain from this village.

540
01:04:34,036 --> 01:04:36,834
And who's going to stop us? You?

541
01:04:37,707 --> 01:04:42,007
Yes. My men and I will.

542
01:04:43,079 --> 01:04:45,309
