your head, Kalia!

545
01:04:56,759 --> 01:04:58,556
Just look around!

546
01:05:14,644 --> 01:05:16,942
Two of them? Is that all?

547
01:05:17,380 --> 01:05:19,405
That's enough for you.

548
01:05:20,116 --> 01:05:23,381
