It's okay now... it certainly is.

584
01:09:16,118 --> 01:09:20,578
Three parts of this now hold
bullets; and three are empty.

585
01:09:21,724 --> 01:09:24,716
I'll just roll the
whole stuff over.

586
01:09:28,297 --> 01:09:34,031
I don't know now where the bullets
are, or where they are not.

587
01:09:34,904 --> 01:09:36,895
I know nothing!

588
01:09:41,377 --> 01:09:49,716
This gun now holds three lives
and three deaths.

589
01:09:52,855 --> 01:09:54,880
Let's see what they get.

590
01:10:02,164 --> 01:10:04,189
He's escaped!

591
01:10:20,983 --> 01:10:23,008
He's escaped, too!

592
01:10:32,194 --> 01:10:34,594
What's gonna happen
of you, Kaliya?

593
01:10:34,964 --> 01:10:38,229
Chief! I've always lived
on what I got from you!

594
01:10:40,269 --> 01:10:44,262
It's time you stopped a bullet.

595
01:10:52,014 --> 01:10:54,039
This is amazing!

596
01:11:06,262 --> 01:11:08,287
All three have escaped!

597
01:11:11,033 --> 01:11:13,365
None of the bastards
stopped a bullet!

598
01:11:40,429 --> 01:11:42,226
All three have escaped!

