01:15:29,424 --> 01:15:33,258
Go away you crazy

615
01:15:37,599 --> 01:15:42,036
Don't tease me you shameless

616
01:15:42,137 --> 01:15:51,170
Ask the world on such occasions only,
the hearts get exchanged

617
01:21:47,636 --> 01:21:52,073
Well... so this is the
Thakur's soldier!

618
01:21:55,944 --> 01:22:00,278
Kaliya told us there
were two of them, Samba.

619
01:22:02,050 --> 01:22:03,881
Where is the other?

620
01:22:04,653 --> 01:22:06,314
Where are you, soldier?!

621
01:22:09,157 --> 01:22:12,649
Hey, soldier... where
is your partner?

622
01:22:13,161 --> 01:22:14,788
Speak up!

623
01:22:15,063 --> 01:22:16,894
Listen, you other soldier!

624
01:22:17,732 --> 01:22:20,758
Will you step out, or do
I gun down your friend here?

625
01:22:21,670 --> 01:22:22,728
Hold it!

626
01:22:25,874 --> 01:22:30,675
Welcome...! Welcome!

627
01:22:32,814 --> 01:22:35,112
We now have you in
our clutches!

628
01:22:37,452 --> 01:22:39,420
Welcome...

629
01:22:42,123 --> 01:22:43,750
Good-boy!

630
01:22:58,373 --> 01:23:04,039
Well, Thakur? You brought these
guys to protect Ramgarh, did you?

631
01:23:04,779 --> 01:23:07,247
To take on Gabbar, did you?

632
01:23:07,882 --> 01:23:12,717
Listen, you villagers!
Take a look out here!

633
01:23:13,054 --> 01:23:16,922
These the guys who came here
to protect you from me!

634
01:23:18,026 --> 01:23:22,122
Have they lost your pluck?
All of it?!

635
01:23:26,468 --> 01:23:31,770
There's only one man who can
save you from Gabbar's wrath!

636
01:23:32,874 --> 01:23:34,899
And that's Gabbar himself!

637
01:23:36,277 --> 01:23:41,476
In exchange for your security, if
we take some provisions from you...

638
01:23:41,883 --> 01:23:43,908
that is no crime or injustice!

639
01:23:44,352 --> 01:23:47,947
No crime, I say!
It's no injustice!

640
01:23:49,257 --> 01:23:56,390
That's it then! Should anyone
dare raise his head again...

641
01:23:56,965 --> 01:23:58,455
I will...

642
01:24:03,104 --> 01:24:05,470
The heads!

643
01:24:07,242 --> 01:24:10,302
You think these guys are
accomplished fighters, don't you?

644
01:24:11,446 --> 01:24:13,414
These hired-gunmen will now...

645
01:24:13,882 --> 01:24:20,219
place their heads on my feet
and beg for mercy!

646
01:24:22,023 --> 01:24:24,048
They will beg at my feet!

647
01:24:29,097 --> 01:24:32,157
You've heard me, haven't you?
You have?

648
01:24:35,036 --> 01:24:38,904
Those heads of yours...
at my feet!

649
01:24:40,809 --> 01:24:42,071
Come on.

650
01:24:43,178 --> 01:24:44,805
Move, I say!

651
