Hurry up, Dhanno!

652
01:27:09,824 --> 01:27:13,521
We can't wage this battle
for you anymore, Thakur!

653
01:27:14,596 --> 01:27:18,532
We held you in great respect.
But it's all over!

654
01:27:19,601 --> 01:27:22,195
We came here for
the brave inspector...

655
01:27:22,704 --> 01:27:26,071
who waged a lone battle against
a gang of bandits in the train.

656
01:27:26,741 --> 01:27:27,308
We didn't come here
for a coward...

657
