We didn't come here
for a coward...

658
01:27:29,043 --> 01:27:32,638
who couldn't pick up a gun lying
before him to save our lives!

659
01:27:35,016 --> 01:27:38,076
It's okay, if you wish to leave.

660
01:27:39,153 --> 01:27:40,814
You can go.

661
01:27:41,022 --> 01:27:46,551
