What reason can there be?
You're a coward!

664
01:27:50,498 --> 01:27:54,025
What reason can there be?
You're a coward!

665
01:28:00,308 --> 01:28:02,299
It's a long story.

666
01:28:03,177 --> 01:28:06,840
It happened during the days I was
posted at the Belapur police station.

667
01:28:07,882 --> 01:28:12,251
We got information that Gabbar was
going to loot the village Haripur.

668
01:28:13,021 --> 01:28:13,621
The police raided them
at the right time...

669
01:28:13,621 --> 01:28:15,054
The police raided them
at the right time...

670
01:28:15,256 --> 01:28:17,281
and the bandits had to flee.

671
01:28:17,825 --> 01:28:20,123
I started chasing Gabbar.

672
01:30:24,252 --> 01:30:29,349
Let me go... let go...
Leave me alone, you bastard!

673
01:30:30,458 --> 01:30:31,726
Gabbar Singh! This is no arm!
This is a noose!

674
01:30:31,726 --> 01:30:34,957
Gabbar Singh! This is no arm!
This is a noose!

675
01:30:36,197 --> 01:30:38,825
In view of the testimonies
and the evidence at hand...

676
01:30:39,066 --> 01:30:41,091
this court reaches
the conclusion that...

677
01:30:41,335 --> 01:30:45,294
Gabbar Singh is a dangerous
and professional criminal.

678
01:30:46,107 --> 01:30:49,167
This court, therefore, holding
him guilty of dacoity...

679
01:30:49,444 --> 01:30:54,347
sentences him to 20 years
of rigorous imprisonment.

680
01:31:00,421 --> 01:31:04,915
I'll remember you...
I'm sure, I will remember you.

681
01:31:05,293 --> 01:31:10,094
After 20 years in the prison,
you will forget everything, Gabbar.

682
01:31:10,498 --> 01:31:13,990
No prison in the world
has walls strong enough...

683
01:31:14,335 --> 01:31:17,099
to hold Gabbar captive
for 20 long years.

684
01:31:18,206 --> 01:31:23,906
And the day I escape...
you will regret it, Thakur.

685
01:31:25,313 --> 01:31:28,214
You're going to regret it.
- Take him away.

686
01:31:28,449 --> 01:31:33,409
This enmity's going to
cost you dear, Thakur!

687
01:31:36,591 --> 01:31:38,786
Thakur! Congratulations!

688
01:31:39,327 --> 01:31:40,862
Another criminal you've nabbed
is coming to my prison.

689
01:31:40,862 --> 01:31:42,329
Another criminal you've nabbed
is coming to my prison.

690
01:31:44,432 --> 01:31:48,163
He's a dangerous man, jailor.
You'd better be careful.

691
01:31:49,604 --> 01:31:52,402
I'm glad your application
for leave has come through.

692
01:31:52,907 --> 01:31:55,967
It had to anyway. You're going on
leave after a very long time.

693
